MBOMBELA –Caser Bernardus de Jager, or Cassie as his family calls him, is still missing after he refused treatment a the Rob Fereira Hospital.  Bernardus was last seen at the Sonpark Spar just after he walked out of the hospital. His family have opened a missing person case and anyone with information on Casper is to contact his brother, Hendry, on 071-684-1042. ALSO READ: The sad trauma of a missing loved one